text: Igor Shesterkin leads the #NYR out for Game 4 warmups
Igor Shesterkin leads the #NYR onto the ice for warmups.
Rangers Igor Shesterkin is pulled in back-to-back starts for the first time in his NHL career.  Tonight is his 100th career NHL start (reg. season + playoffs)
